rc=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係。一早同佢講過話如果有一日分手嘅話，一定係佢衰，而唔係唔愛佢。"},{"pid":"734a8ed4fc2191fa62f3eb9d7d7b836cbc5b00ff","tid":894232,"uid":136027,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T07:42:21.000Z","msg":"on9繼續想扑你啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真愛由一開始就唔會傷害你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e0cd195c5d55e9fb1aff4d1b29610436915b8cf","tid":894232,"uid":182774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T10:35:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9c3392b9624b8974fac0089ec71a8f90d78f01a0","tid":894232,"uid":205566,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T10:43:16.000Z","msg":"咁愛你都要愛自己架下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢都話會改，你係都要分開<br />\n你覺得佢仲可以點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f40d6ae186d39f830aa202cb48c63eb23a3c017","tid":894232,"uid":91767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T11:11:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>on9繼續想扑你啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真愛由一開始就唔會傷害你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有時佢忍唔到啲脾氣"},{"pid":"aff0b841ed1963f5f59c427e615cd1371b45fd8a","tid":894232,"uid":91767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T11:12:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁愛你都要愛自己架下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢都話會改，你係都要分開<br />\n你覺得佢仲可以點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所以而家咪俾機會佢，同返佢一齊囉。而且自己又真係好愛佢"},{"pid":"1e49c25d595adc5bda3308f02e64f3fae82e4d11","tid":894232,"uid":140590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b052788437f3d59c61e6f6fa8d0ef62c8e30ef0","tid":894232,"uid":91767,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T09:13:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote